19
00:00:18,272 --> 00:00:20,024
<i>Evil alliance!</i>

20
00:00:20,191 --> 00:00:22,276
<i>Darth Maul and Savage Opress</i>

21
00:00:22,401 --> 00:00:25,446
<i>escape Obi-Wan Kenobi's assault
once again.</i>

22
00:00:26,072 --> 00:00:29,116
<i>With their plan to build
a crime organization in peril,</i>

23
00:00:29,242 --> 00:00:32,078
<i>the brothers' fate is about
to be changed forever</i>

24
00:00:32,119 --> 00:00:36,040
<i>as they drift barely alive
through unknown space.</i>

25
00:01:18,583 --> 00:01:20,084
What are you?

26
00:01:20,876 --> 00:01:22,044
Should we rub them out?

27
00:01:22,128 --> 00:01:23,170
No.

28
00:01:23,254 --> 00:01:25,423
I want to hear their story.

29
00:01:25,715 --> 00:01:29,176
If they're an enemy of the Jedi
then they're a friend of mine.

30
00:01:29,260 --> 00:01:30,678
Load 'em up.

31
00:02:57,556 --> 00:02:59,183
Savage.

32
00:03:08,109 --> 00:03:11,028
You're not Jedi, so what are you?

33
00:03:15,783 --> 00:03:18,452
We are Sith.

34
00:03:19,578 --> 00:03:21,956
Do you serve Count Dooku?

35
00:03:22,123 --> 00:03:24,125
I serve no one.

36
00:03:24,959 --> 00:03:29,296
I thought there could only be two Sith,
a master and an apprentice?

37
00:03:30,464 --> 00:03:35,302
We are brothers.
The true Lords of the Sith.

38
00:03:36,429 --> 00:03:37,805
What happened to your ship?

39
00:03:37,972 --> 00:03:40,808
Destroyed by Jedi.

40
00:03:40,975 --> 00:03:42,393
Do you know which Jedi?

41
00:03:42,476 --> 00:03:44,603
Kenobi.

42
00:03:48,149 --> 00:03:50,651
And what do you seek now, Sith?

43
00:03:50,776 --> 00:03:53,988
Fortune and power.

44
00:03:54,655 --> 00:03:58,743
Repair this one's legs
and do what you can for the other.

45
00:03:58,826 --> 00:04:00,119
Yes, sir.

46
00:04:07,626 --> 00:04:09,670
Go on. Get moving.

47
00:04:16,802 --> 00:04:20,014
In time for tea. Come join me.

48
00:04:25,978 --> 00:04:30,858
Made with the florets of a Cassius tree.
It's good for your health.

49
00:04:37,823 --> 00:04:39,325
Your mark?

50
00:04:39,366 --> 00:04:43,496
The sign of Clan Vizsla. I am Pre Vizsla.

51
00:04:43,537 --> 00:04:45,164
We are the Death Watch,

52
00:04:45,206 --> 00:04:49,627
descendants of the true warrior faith
all Mandalorians once knew.

53
00:04:49,710 --> 00:04:54,215
Now my people are living in exile
because we will not abandon our heritage.

54
00:04:54,381 --> 00:04:58,511
Our people were warriors. Strong, feared.

55
00:04:59,136 --> 00:05:01,222
Now they're ruled by the new Mandalorians

56
00:05:01,305 --> 00:05:04,391
who think that being a pacifist
is a good thing.

57
00:05:04,475 --> 00:05:08,521
They've given away our honor
and tradition for peace.

58
00:05:09,647 --> 00:05:13,317
Duchess Satine and her corrupt leadership
are crushing our souls,

59
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,652
destroying our identity.

60
00:05:15,569 --> 00:05:17,404
That is our struggle.

61
00:05:18,322 --> 00:05:21,575
If they are weak, why do you wait?

62
00:05:21,742 --> 00:05:26,705
The Duchess has powerful allies,
including your Jedi friend, Kenobi.

63
00:05:28,624 --> 00:05:31,877
He is also responsible for our exile.

64
00:05:32,586 --> 00:05:34,922
Perhaps fortune brought us together.

65
00:05:35,881 --> 00:05:38,384
It is the will of the Force.

66
00:05:38,801 --> 00:05:42,555
We can help you reclaim Mandalore.

67
00:05:42,596 --> 00:05:45,641
And punish Kenobi for his trespasses.

68
00:05:46,475 --> 00:05:51,647
We allied ourselves with Sith before.
Count Dooku, he betrayed us.

69
00:05:51,772 --> 00:05:53,315
Sith are no better than Jedi.

70
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:55,317
They claim to be powerful,

71
00:05:55,442 --> 00:05:58,988
but we put these two back together
after the Jedi gutted them.

72
00:05:59,905 --> 00:06:03,325
Doubt will only lead to failure.

73
00:06:04,910 --> 00:06:06,120
Hold!

74
00:06:06,287 --> 00:06:12,501
Our combined strength will be rewarded.
Mandalore will be yours, and Kenobi,

75
00:06:13,127 --> 00:06:15,170
this Sith pretender, Dooku,

76
00:06:15,296 --> 00:06:19,508
and all our enemies will fall.

77
00:06:22,761 --> 00:06:25,764
Check on your brother.
We'll put it to a vote.

78
00:06:48,621 --> 00:06:51,665
Rest, apprentice. You're safe.

79
00:06:56,503 --> 00:07:01,800
Our crash was discovered by enemies of
the Jedi, and we are in their care.

80
00:07:03,552 --> 00:07:05,179
Are we prisoners?

81
00:07:05,304 --> 00:07:06,513
No.

82
00:07:07,473 --> 00:07:08,682
Allies.

83
00:07:09,058 --> 00:07:11,852
They have much to offer,
including their planet.

84
00:07:11,977 --> 00:07:17,149
They are strong, and unlike pirates,
they possess honor.

85
00:07:17,232 --> 00:07:19,485
Another weakness.

86
00:07:19,526 --> 00:07:25,532
They know nothing of our intentions.
Those revelations will come too late.

87
00:07:32,206 --> 00:07:34,166
I see you have your strength back.

88
00:07:43,050 --> 00:07:45,052
I never got your names.

89
00:07:45,177 --> 00:07:48,555
I am Maul, this is Savage.

90
00:07:49,390 --> 00:07:53,102
Our brothers are in favor of an alliance
to liberate Mandalore.

91
00:07:53,227 --> 00:07:58,899
This Duchess of yours will soon discover
the true burden of peace.

92
00:08:11,078 --> 00:08:13,580
Your people are strong and skilled,

93
00:08:13,706 --> 00:08:17,084
but you will need an army
to free Mandalore.

94
00:08:17,751 --> 00:08:20,295
There are more on Mandalore
who will join us.

95
00:08:20,421 --> 00:08:22,423
Their help would come too late.

96
00:08:22,548 --> 00:08:26,468
We can assemble an army
beginning with the Black Sun.

97
00:08:26,593 --> 00:08:30,431
They're a crime syndicate.
Hardly a force to rally with.

98
00:08:30,597 --> 00:08:33,142
The can provide us with
the resources we need

99
00:08:33,267 --> 00:08:37,896
to sustain a war without the scrutiny
of the Republic.

100
00:09:29,114 --> 00:09:30,866
A battalion, Brother.

101
00:09:30,991 --> 00:09:33,827
They will serve us well.

102
00:09:37,164 --> 00:09:40,167
We request an audience with your leaders.

103
00:09:40,334 --> 00:09:42,461
It'll be your funeral.

104
00:10:03,023 --> 00:10:05,526
Why do you come here?

105
00:10:05,651 --> 00:10:07,986
We seek an army.

106
00:10:08,028 --> 00:10:11,573
Fools. We are not mercenaries.

107
00:10:11,698 --> 00:10:16,036
Dispose of them.
Keep their ships and weapons.

108
00:10:16,578 --> 00:10:18,205
Give me that one's sword.

109
00:10:31,426 --> 00:10:34,721
This is your last opportunity to join us.

110
00:10:34,805 --> 00:10:35,889
Quiet!

111
00:10:36,723 --> 00:10:38,725
We are the Black Sun!

112
00:10:44,731 --> 00:10:45,899
Hmm.

113
00:10:46,233 --> 00:10:47,901
Very well, then.

114
00:11:05,252 --> 00:11:09,923
It would seem the decision
to join us is now yours.

115
00:11:10,090 --> 00:11:14,178
After careful consideration,
we will join you.

116
00:11:14,261 --> 00:11:16,305
Show us your supplies.

117
00:11:31,445 --> 00:11:35,991
We have our army now.
I have a plan to undermine Satine.

118
00:11:36,783 --> 00:11:41,371
The army is weak.
We are not ready for the Duchess.

119
00:11:41,997 --> 00:11:45,000
With my plan,
we won't need a bigger force.

120
00:11:45,375 --> 00:11:49,463
There is only one plan, one vision.

121
00:11:49,713 --> 00:11:52,674
And it belongs to Death Watch.

122
00:11:52,799 --> 00:11:55,052
Your vision lacks clarity.

123
00:11:55,135 --> 00:12:00,724
Without us, you have no army
and no reason to replace the Duchess.

124
00:12:03,143 --> 00:12:08,315
The depth of this opportunity eludes you.
You shall watch and learn.

125
00:12:40,847 --> 00:12:42,391
More criminals.

126
00:12:42,516 --> 00:12:46,395
Spice dealers connected
to all the crime families of Coruscant.

127
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:50,399
The Pykes. They will be the next to join us.

128
00:12:52,192 --> 00:12:54,903
We know you've been forming an army.

129
00:12:55,028 --> 00:12:57,531
Were you expecting us?

130
00:12:57,572 --> 00:13:03,036
Underworld's a small community.
I have no desire to oppose you.

131
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:05,539
We come to join you.

132
00:13:07,374 --> 00:13:08,959
Very good.

133
00:13:09,042 --> 00:13:13,213
Then ready our troops.
We leave for Nal Hutta immediately.

134
00:13:29,396 --> 00:13:33,900
There are many things the Hutts influence
and possess that would be useful to us.

135
00:13:36,570 --> 00:13:38,155
We have no credits.

136
00:13:42,743 --> 00:13:47,914
Your lives, in exchange for Hutt space
and everything in its borders.

137
00:15:11,206 --> 00:15:14,042
I see negotiations have gone as planned.

138
00:15:14,126 --> 00:15:15,544
Secure this platform.

139
00:15:33,770 --> 00:15:35,605
Retreat! Retreat! Back inside!

140
00:16:17,731 --> 00:16:18,815
Hey!

141
00:17:13,161 --> 00:17:15,080
Come on, let's get out of here!

142
00:17:20,043 --> 00:17:24,548
Let them go. They're only bounty hunters,
they have no allegiance.

143
00:17:33,223 --> 00:17:36,560
Sir, the Hutts have escaped. Except one.

144
00:17:40,689 --> 00:17:42,482
Where are the others?

145
00:17:48,738 --> 00:17:50,031
Kill him.

146
00:17:50,156 --> 00:17:51,199
Oh!

147
00:17:56,746 --> 00:17:58,373
Give me a location.

148
00:17:59,332 --> 00:18:01,835
Tatooine, Tatooine!

149
00:18:02,210 --> 00:18:04,087
Jabba's palace.

150
00:18:05,255 --> 00:18:11,303
So the only thing that you can tell me
is that I will find Jabba at Jabba's palace?

151
00:19:35,428 --> 00:19:38,098
Give up, Jabba, you're the only ones left.

152
00:19:39,432 --> 00:19:41,601
Submit or suffer.

153
00:19:51,027 --> 00:19:55,532
The mighty Jabba and the Hutt families
have decided to join you.

154
00:20:10,296 --> 00:20:12,632
Between the Hutts, Black Sun,
and the Pykes,

155
00:20:12,716 --> 00:20:15,844
we'll have a large reserve
of muscle and supplies.

156
00:20:15,969 --> 00:20:17,011
Yes.

157
00:20:17,762 --> 00:20:20,765
Then Mandalore and Kenobi
are still our priority?

158
00:20:20,932 --> 00:20:22,767
They are vital.

159
00:20:22,809 --> 00:20:25,687
I'm curious to hear the rest of your plan.

160
00:20:25,979 --> 00:20:30,483
The vision has expanded.
You will still rule Mandalore,

161
00:20:30,525 --> 00:20:35,447
and under your protection,
I will command a new galactic underworld.

162
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:44,330
Mandalore influences a league
of 2,000 neutral systems.

163
00:20:44,372 --> 00:20:47,959
It gives you a great deal of options
for your enterprise.

164
00:20:48,001 --> 00:20:51,129
You have learned
from your previous oversights.

165
00:20:51,171 --> 00:20:56,634
With their combined forces, the Republic
and the Separatists will be irrelevant.

166
00:20:56,676 --> 00:20:58,344
Then, are we ready?

167
00:20:58,845 --> 00:21:02,724
Mobilize the army.
Send an advance guard to the capital.

168
00:21:02,849 --> 00:21:06,811
I want a list of targets vital
to Mandalore's security.

169
00:21:06,853 --> 00:21:11,149
Choose wisely.
There will be no second chances.

170
00:21:22,368 --> 00:21:25,872
Stay focused.
Mandalore will soon be ours,

171
00:21:25,997 --> 00:21:30,043
and Maul and his brother will be dead
alongside the Duchess.

172
00:21:30,067 --> 00:21:35,067
http://hiqve.com/

